"></div>\n<div class=\"ss1\"></div>\n<img src=\"../../images/weixintupian_20210224160842.jpg\">\n  \n  <div class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n流体力学研究所</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/gclxx.htm\">工程力学系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/F/1D/8D/6F6490DDCEF28CB3320F1F99DA1_8DD9F495_1216.jpg?e=.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>彭杰</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                    <p>职称：副研究员</p>\n                                    <p>电话：+86-10-62772729</p>\n                                    <p>E-mail address：peng-jie@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">个人简介</div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_img\">1974年生，云南昆明人，工学博士，副研究员。</p>\n<p>联系方式：</p>\n<p>电话：+86-10-62772729</p>\n<p>E-mail：peng-jie@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n<p>办公室： 清华大学逸夫科技楼1504</p>\n<p>邮编： 100084</p>\n<p>承担以下课程教学工作</p>\n<p>流体力学（研究生）</p>\n<p>高等流体力学（研究生）</p>\n<p>格子气自动机和格子Boltzmann 方法（研究生）</p>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>1992.09 - 1997.07 清华大学工程力学系（流体力学） 获工学学士学位<br></p>\n<p>1995.09 - 1997.07 清华大学经济管理学院（企业管理） 获经济学学士学位</p>\n<p>1997.09 - 1999.12 清华大学工程力学系（流体力学） 获工学硕士学位</p>\n<p>1999.12 - 2002.07 清华大学工程力学系（流体力学）</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作履历</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>2003.01 - 2004.12 清华大学动力工程与工程热物理博士后流动站 博士后</p>\n<p>2005.05 - 2008.03 韩国三星集团高等综合技术研究院 访问学者、高级研究员</p>\n<p>2008.04 -至 今 清华大学航天航空学院 副研究员</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>流动稳定性、多场耦合问题；</p>\n<p>非牛顿流体流体流动特性；</p>\n<p>界面流特性和流动稳定性；</p>\n<p>燃料电池设计及建模；</p>\n<p>在研项目</p>\n<p>无膜微型燃料电池流动特性及稳定性机理研究，自然科学基金10972115，负责</p>\n<p>极大规模集成电路制造装备及成套工艺，国家科技重大专项，参与</p>\n<p>完成项目</p>\n<p>屈服应力流体螺旋Couette流动稳定性研究，自然科学基金10402016，负责</p>\n<p>粘塑性流体螺旋Couette流动特性及稳定性的究，博士后基金2004035062，负责</p>\n<p>高剪切速率下电流变液的流动特性研究，自然科学基金10472054，参与</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>发表论文30余篇，申请专利10余项，其中</p>\n<p>代表性论著</p>\n<p>[1] Peng J, Zhu KQ (2011): Instability of the interface in co-extrusion flow of two UCM fluids in the presence of surfactant,<i>JOURNAL OF NON-NEWTONIAN FLUID MECHANICS</i>166:152-163</p>\n<p>[2]Peng J, Zhu KQ (2010): Numerical simulation of Taylor Couette flow of Bingham fluids,<i>JOURNAL OF NON-NEWTONIAN FLUID MECHANICS</i>165:1161-1170</p>\n<p>[3]Peng J, Zhu KQ (2010): Linear instability of two-fluid Taylor-Couette flow in the presence of surfactant,<i>JOURNAL OF FLUID MECHANICS</i> 651:357-385</p>\n<p>[4]Peng J, Shin JY, Song TW (2008): Transient response of high temperature PEM fuel cell,<i>JOURNAL OF POWER SOURCES</i>, 179:220-231</p>\n<p>[5]Peng J, Lee SJ (2006): Numerical simulation of proton exchange membrane fuel cells with high operating temperature,<i>JOURNAL OF POWER SOURCES</i>, 162(2): 1182-1191</p>\n<p>[6]Peng J, Zhu KQ (2006): Drag force of interacting coaxial spheres in viscoplastic fluids,<i>JOURNAL OF NON-NEWTONIAN FLUID MECHANICS</i>135(2&amp;3):83-91</p>\n<p>[7]Peng J, Zhu KQ (2006): Effects of electric field on hydrodynamic characteristics of finite-length ER journal bearings,<i>TRIBOLOGY INTERNATIONAL</i>39:533-540</p>\n<p>[8]Peng J, Zhu KQ (2004): Linear instability of Bingham fluid in spiral Couette flow,<i>JOURNAL OF FLUID MECHANICS</i>, 512:21-46</p>\n<p>已获授权专利</p>\n<p>[1] Peng J, Lee SJ, Song TW, Shin JY, Bipolar plate for fuel cell, Korean Patent, Registration No. 1007181130000</p>\n<p>[2] Peng J, Song TW, Lee SJ, Shin JY, Fuel cell providing stack which has improved sealing structure, Korean Patent, Registration No. 1008132460000</p>\n<p>[3] Peng J, Lee SJ, Song TW, Shin JY, Bipolar plate and fuel cell providing stack including the same, Korean Patent, Registration No. 1007457420000</p>\n<p>[4] Shin JY, Peng J, Lee SJ, Song TW, A cooling plate providing improved channel, Korean Patent, Registration No. 1007457380000</p>\n<p>[5] Song TW, Lee SJ, Peng J, Shin JY, Sealing member of cooling plate for fuel cell stack, Korean Patent, Registration No. 1008031950000</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">[6]彭杰，李承宰，宋泰元，慎宰英，用于燃料电池的双极板，中国发明专利，专利号: ZL 200610121559.5</p></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left footer-logo\">                            <img src=\"../../images/logo.png\">\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pull-right footer-txt\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>版权所有 © 清华大学京ICP备15006448号 京公网安备 110402430053 号&nbsp;</p><p>推荐ie8以上谷歌等浏览器浏览网页</p><p>联系方式：电话：010-62782434&nbsp; &nbsp;传真：010-62792407</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n<script src=\"../../js/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/slick.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/wow.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/common.js\"></script>\n<script>\nif (!(/msie [6|7|8|9]/i.test(navigator.userAgent))){\n  new WOW().init();\n};\n            \n       function stopPropagation(e) {\n            var ev = e || window.event;\n            if (ev.stopPropagation) {\n                ev.stopPropagation();\n            }\n            else if (window.event) {\n                window.event.cancelBubble = true;//兼容IE\n            }\n        }\n        $(\".search-a\").click(function (e) {\n          if($(\".search-box\").is(\":hidden\"))\n          {\n            $(\".search-box\").slideDown(\"slow\"); \n             stopPropagation(e);\n          }else{\n            $(\".search-box\").slideUp(\"slow\");\n    